ActIndian Act
SubjectPasqua First Nation - 1906 Surrender Specific Claim Settlement ** Agreement **
PrecisOrder (1) authorizing the Minister to execute, on behalf of Her Majesty in Right of Canada, the PASQUA FIRST NATION 1906 SURRENDER SPECIFIC CLAIM SETTLEMENT AGREEMENT between Canada and the Pasqua First Nation; and (2) accepting the absolute surrender to Canada of all rights and interest of the lands.
